From 3df174f0274ac9008a2b522ad7d6089f714fdf77 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <noreply@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 16 Jul 2026 04:59:08 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] Make completed/inactive campaigns fully editable
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit

Remove pointer-events-none and readOnly from inactive campaign
accordion content — all fields now editable with autosave,
same as active campaigns.

Co-Authored-By: Claude Sonnet 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>
Claude-Session: https://claude.ai/code/session_01VDhwXDyc6xaUka1ouA3hGU
